%% Sequence - Search route flow

sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant Frontend
  participant Backend
  participant GIS as GIS/DB

  User->>Frontend: Enter origin/destination
  Frontend->>Backend: POST /search {coords/query}
  Backend->>GIS: Spatial query / nearest routes
  GIS-->>Backend: route candidates
  Backend->>Backend: Rank & format results
  Backend-->>Frontend: 200 OK {results}
  Frontend-->>User: Display map + list
